determined and fixed by the courts, and indemnities arising from work accidents and occupational illnesses covered, the policy also covers
payment of all costs relating to medical treatment, pharmaceutical or hospital expenses resulting from work related accidents.**The medical insurance includes:**- Transit risk;
- Professional Illness;
- Medical Expenses;
- Permanent Disability;
- Temporary Total Disability;**Exclusion:**- The accidents, the victims of which are those performing their work in
  their own homes;
- The accidents resulting from loss of the use or mental capacity by the
  injured person, drunkenness or other similar causes;
- The accidents sustained by those who render services for which they
